{"tid":330470,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"做膠錯但又搞笑既同事","createTime":"2017-07-21T08:47:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-21T13:19:19.000Z","uid":77363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8a501d82726c1838d321fc7dea205185878fe74d","tid":330470,"uid":77363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T08:47:57.000Z","msg":"不如大家分享下同事既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 野<br />\n<br />\n我公司有個新助理，grad了3年，係呢到番左兩個月工，有日叫佢2:30前打去比人傾少少urgent野，佢4點先同我講佢頭先唔識點打電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，試到2:50先醒起搵旁邊同事幫佢打通個電話，但係已經太遲對方已走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n果個係一個香港2字頭普通電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 打電話既方法只係拎起電話打9+2xxxxxxx, 佢番左兩個月工都唔識打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e61a2b44bf5204a7d4ff282344b2efb81e988fe","tid":330470,"uid":43231,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T09:06:39.000Z","msg":"兩個月都唔識㩒街線？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cc3da74dde5a7f4c6e5b06da90675bbdd1bf967","tid":330470,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T09:12:52.000Z","msg":"返兩個月都唔識打都唔算咩 可能真係未用過<br />\n之但係2:30試二十分鐘到2:50先問到同事打到過去？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n二十分鐘&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"20f7602d04c7866d81a5ee3aaf33003ec3b1b303","tid":330470,"uid":77363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T09:19:48.000Z","msg":"附近係有3-4個同事係到做野，就算唔識用公司電話，手提都得啦...<br />\n<br />\n又或者佢可以即刻同我講，唔係個幾鐘後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee35d53a153bea0833e30d363bdf3866479f32f7","tid":330470,"uid":15208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T10:47:59.000Z","msg":"你仲搞笑啦，咁都唔炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b20553fdc4b77b62d4875292bcf72c04d18bd4ba","tid":330470,"uid":121029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T12:03:57.000Z","msg":"分享一個）<br />\n返左成年工，都記唔到公司開門密碼，企左係門口on99咁等人開。<br />\n<br />\n利申：個密碼得四粒字仲要係乘數表𠴱d配搭，成年冇換過密碼。"},{"pid":"a31cb7d31fd88dece98d46086bc195cd2c2df8ce","tid":330470,"uid":77363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T13:02:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你仲搞笑啦，咁都唔炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我老闆都係閪人，是L但比人你就算，人哋做唔到嘢咪你做埋囉，炒條毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有一日佢仲搞笑啊，我哋有個deadline個個做到踢晒腳，佢咩都做錯（最簡單出email比客夠膽死一句句子入面中文又有英文又有）所以我畀左其他人既濕星野佢做，根住佢原本果份我地其他人一齊做埋，佢以為我蝦佢，夠膽死send email cc  老闆話本來人哋嘅野我叫佢做好唔公平，仲叫嗰位同事（都係佢上司）自己做返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n睇到真係笑出黎，本身我都唔想搞大件事幫佢做咗算，d人真係自<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0dac09570c29291e49104ece564ee008d0ff825","tid":330470,"uid":50165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T13:19:19.000Z","msg":"大大聲係個group 講啲貨唔岩數，點知係自己mark 漏左"}]}